Description: # Introduction
        
        Welcome to laze, a ninja build file generator.
        
        # Requirements
        
        - python3
        - click
        - pyyaml
        - ninja
        
            $ "pip3 install --user click pyyaml"
            $ sudo apt-get install ninja
        
